Monitor NXDOMAIN spikes

ðŸ”¥ 8. What is split-horizon DNS and how is it implemented in Route 53?
Definition:

Same domain resolves differently internally vs externally.

Implementation:

Create Public Hosted Zone

Create Private Hosted Zone with same name

Attach private zone to VPC

Internal â†’ Private IP
External â†’ Public IP

