ðŸ”¥ 14. How does Alias record differ from CNAME?

Alias:

AWS-native

Works at zone apex

Free

Points to ALB, CloudFront, S3

CNAME:

Standard DNS

Cannot be root domain

Extra DNS lookup

ðŸ”¥ 15. What are failure modes of Route 53?

TTL caching delays failover

Health check false positives

Resolver misbehavior

ISP ignoring TTL

DNS poisoning risks (if DNSSEC not enabled)

ðŸ”¥ 16. Explain DNSSEC support in Route 53.

DNSSEC:

Cryptographic signature for DNS records

Prevents spoofing

Uses KSK and ZSK

Tradeoffs:

More complexity

Slightly increased response size

Requires registrar support

ðŸ”¥ 17. How do you migrate DNS between providers with zero downtime?

Steps:

Lower TTL (48 hrs before)

Sync records

Validate new provider

Switch NS records

Monitor propagation

ðŸ”¥ 18. What is the difference between NS delegation and subdomain delegation?

NS delegation:

Delegate child zone to another DNS provider

Used in:

Multi-account

Multi-team architecture

Cross-organization DNS ownership

